CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page A20, reads: "Foster B. Hartman, sales manager, poses with Miss Helen Currier sales trainer, in Stauffer Home Reducing Plan booth."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of three women standing, including Helen Currier possibly on right or left, standing in Stauffer Home Reducing Plan booth in Syria Mosque for the 1956 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
